    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This is, without exaggeration, the finest example of this model currently on the market. From the moment you approach the vehicle, the factory-original paint gleams with a deep, mirror-like luster, free of even the smallest swirl marks or stone chips. Every body panel aligns with surgical precision, and the alloy wheels are absolutely flawless, wrapped in premium rubber with nearly full tread. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the hand-stitched leather upholstery still carries that distinct new-car aroma, showing zero signs of wear, creasing, or sun fading. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced navigation, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively by certified technicians. This is more than a used car; it is a collector-grade timepiece preserved in peak condition. If you demand perfection, your search ends here.",
      "price": 48900.0,
